{"title":"Puzzles","markdown":{"yaml":{"title":"Puzzles","comments":false,"toc":false},"containsRefs":false,"markdown":"\n\n<p class=\"project-page-intro\">\nPractice tracks for sharpening GPU programming, ML systems intuition,\nalgorithmic problem solving, and quantitative reasoning.\n</p>\n\n<div class=\"project-category-grid\">\n  <a class=\"project-category-card\" href=\"https://leetgpu.com/#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"project-card-kicker\">GPU Programming</span>\n    <span class=\"project-card-title\">LeetGPU</span>\n    <span class=\"project-card-description\">\n      Browser-based GPU programming challenges for building comfort with kernels, memory movement, and parallel execution.\n    </span>\n    <span class=\"project-card-tags\">\n      <span>GPU</span>\n      <span>Kernels</span>\n      <span>Practice</span>\n    </span>\n  </a>\n\n  <a class=\"project-category-card\" href=\"https://tensara.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"project-card-kicker\">Tensor Systems</span>\n    <span class=\"project-card-title\">Tensara</span>\n    <span class=\"project-card-description\">\n      Tensor and systems-oriented exercises for practicing the reasoning patterns behind modern AI workloads.\n    </span>\n    <span class=\"project-card-tags\">\n      <span>Tensors</span>\n      <span>Systems</span>\n      <span>AI</span>\n    </span>\n  </a>\n\n  <a class=\"project-category-card\" href=\"https://puzzles.modular.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"project-card-kicker\">Mojo / GPU</span>\n    <span class=\"project-card-title\">Mojo GPU Puzzles</span>\n    <span class=\"project-card-description\">\n      Hands-on GPU puzzles in Mojo for learning kernel structure, memory hierarchy, and accelerator programming.\n    </span>\n    <span class=\"project-card-tags\">\n      <span>Mojo</span>\n      <span>GPU</span>\n      <span>Kernels</span>\n    </span>\n  </a>\n\n  <a class=\"project-category-